thread.title: Tom Killeen
thread.title_full: Interparcel Australia reviewed by Tom Killeen

author: Tom Killeen
title: Tom Killeen
text:
I needed to return a golf club to the USA and was given a crazy price from another carrier which was simply way too expensive.
I found Interparcel on the Internet and was pleasantly surprised with their price for exactly the same service.
Their system was easy to follow and they communicated well.
The parcel was delivered promptly and I actually received the name of the person who received it in USA.
I would use Interparcel again for sure.
Tom Killeen
Australia
